snippet: Victoria Azarenka lost in her first match in more than three months in the first round of the Aegon Championships in Eastbourne, England.
abstract: Camila Giorgi defeats Victoria Azarenka in first round of the Aegon Championships, first loss for the tennis star in more than three months.
lead_paragraph: Victoria Azarenka lost in her first match in more than three months in the first round of the Aegon Championships in Eastbourne, England.
